### ── apps/api/requests/contributions.http ────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = <paste_donor_access_token_here>
 
### Create a contribution (Donor only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/contributions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "programId": "seed-program-001",
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "notes": "Monthly recurring donation"
}
 
### List my contributions (Donor sees own only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/contributions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
 
### Get single contribution
GET {{baseUrl}}/contributions/<contribution_id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
